{"tid":1794161,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"劉達邦：剛過去周末餐飲業情況好轉 料假日零售暢旺","createTime":"2019-12-23T02:17:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T02:22:27.000Z","uid":301585,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f89ca9335bb7c94ae3ad5bc251f70e23d3753226","tid":1794161,"uid":301585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T02:17:24.000Z","msg":"2019-12-23 HKT 09:32<br />\n香港中小型企業聯合會榮譽主席劉達邦認為，政府推出多輪紓困措施有「少少幫助」，又指近兩星期混亂情況減少，剛過去的周末餐飲業情況好轉，由於聖誕節臨近，估計零售方面未來數天會暢旺。<br />\n劉達邦在本台節目《千禧年代》說，仍要視乎未來1個月會否再出現混亂，否則業界一定遇到結業潮，但亦要視乎經營者的財政背景，縱使借錢予有關企業，若生意不多，反而會導致他們債台高築。<br />\n飲食界立法會議員張宇人在同一節目表示，踏入12月餐飲業的情況較前兩個月為佳，但這個月情況較去年同期仍有所下跌。他說，到餐廳用膳的人數及平均消費都減少，又指昨日冬至，感覺菜單價格較以往便宜，估計飲食界整體生意減少3成。<br />\n張宇人又說，目前農曆新年的餐廳訂枱情況慘淡，相信節日後會有餐廳倒閉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499132-20191223.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499132-20191223.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwQPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=096ce89f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499132-20191223.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=03d0b28d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499132-20191223.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n仆街啦香港人，有ｄ骨氣得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37f7212606217a477f3e359df96984ef2a50db7e","tid":1794161,"uid":153600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T02:18:39.000Z","msg":"唔使驚<br />\n聖誕嗰兩日<br />\n你哋就知死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b063864d952228efd1002b9758f4cfb7bd3e7905","tid":1794161,"ui